Difference between synchronized and Lock?

synchronized	                 Lock

Implicit	                     Explicit
No try	                         tryLock
Auto release	                 Manual release
Less flexible	                 More flexible


Example:

Lock lock = new ReentrantLock();
lock.lock();

try {
   // critical section
} finally {
   lock.unlock();
}

Scenario:

You want timeout while waiting for lock. What to use?

